body:
Heartxxy adds several breeding related patterns to Hex Casting:

Normal Spells:
- Breed, which puts an animal in love;
- Nurture, which ages a creature as if fed by hand;
- Cron's Purification, which returns the age of a creature;

Great Spells:
- Greater Breed, which instantly splits an eligible mob into two children. Ineligible ones are evaporated into a handful of media instead.
